Tvvo letters from the agents of the five regiments of horse, the one to the whole souldiery of the Army, the other to some who sent unto them, to receive further information and satisfaction. Everard, Robert, fl. 1664.
8 p.
s.n., [London : 1647]
Caption title. Signed on A4r: Robert Everard [and 11 others]. Imprint from Wing. Annotation on Thomason copy: "8ber [i.e. October] 28 1647". Reproduction of the original in the British Library.
